!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %h1 Welcome to Blueprint!
    %p
      Hey #{@user.name},
    %p
      An account has been created for you on the Blueprint website. To access it, go to either
      %a{:href => "http://www.calblueprint.org/"} calblueprint.org
      or
      %a{:href => "http://bptech.berkeley.edu/"} bptech.berkeley.edu
      and click on the hidden "Sign In" button at the top right of the nav-bar. Your credentials are:
    %p
      email: #{@user.email}
      %br/
      password: #{@password}
    %p
      Once you're in, please change your password and update your bio so that the public can see you on our
      %a{:href => "http://bptech.berkeley.edu/team"} Team
      page!
    %p
      Cheers!
      %br/
      \-The Blueprint Team
